column5: Anybody heard from the "BAMA" dog lately? Not like him to miss a couple days--kinda miss that comeback style of his.  Who knows he is from the south--maybe he's takin up the shine runnin biz to fill his days.  Bushart
"Miss a couple days"... he was here last night doin his usual stirrin .....   Maybe that all got removed and appears he was absent! LOL
He was also here for a while this morning and also posted. I won't tell him you were looking for him though. He enjoys the abuse.
I'm here, I'm here!!!... I know I've been slacking on my "comeback" chores, so I'll drink and extra rum and try to make up for it this evenin'!
